    • Method Detail

      • reply

        void reply​(Object data)
        Asynchronously invokes an FA callback (on the JavaScript side) to pass data from this PA.

        If you pass an Array or Collection, the JavaScript side automatically expands the array or collection in the sequence of the parameter list of the JavaScript (FA) callback.

        Parameters:
        data - Indicates the data to pass to the FA callback.
        Since:
        4
